                  </svg>
                  Select student work.
                </dt>
                <dd class="inline">Connect to Google Drive and select the student work you want to grade.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-blue-600">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 12 3.269 3.125A59.769 59.769 0 0 1 21.485 12 59.768 59.768 0 0 1 3.27 20.875L5.999 12Zm0 0h7.5" />
                  </svg>
                  Review and finalize.
                </dt>
                <dd class="inline">GradeBot will provide detailed feedback for each student and build an assignment summary report for you. You review and send the feedback to students.</dd>
              </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start justify-end lg:order-first">
        <img src="<%= asset_path('how-it-works.png') %>" alt="Product screenshot" class="w-[24rem] max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 sm:w-[36rem]" width="2432" height="1442">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
